## Installation

1) Copy CSmartyViewRender.php into:
framework/web/renderers
2) Download a copy of Smarty 2.x and put it into:
framework/web/renderers/smarty/
3) To use CSmartyViewRenderer, configure it as an application component named "viewRenderer" in the application configuration:

array(
	'components' => array(
			......
			'viewRenderer' => array(
				'class' => 'CSmartyViewRenderer',
		),
	),
)

4) Go run your application